  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:blockquote>My main research interests are the Grothendieck construction and its generalizations, enriched category theory, 2-category theory and 2-categorical elementary topoi. I am also interested in applying category theory to logic, geometry and computer science.</fr:blockquote>
